      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in mint condition. The exterior is clean with no visible dents, scratches, or paint issues. The interior shows no wear \u2014 upholstery and all surfaces are in like-new condition. Mechanically, the engine runs smoothly, all systems function properly, and there are no known issues. Service history is up to date.",
